            "title": "鋼鐵版白蛇傳︱機械人許仙、白素貞  杭州西湖浪漫邂逅",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"機械人版的白素貞與許仙現身西湖，引起關注。抖音\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f060443b3eb32d3c663e87ad1442de79/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250309/_2025030920302875527.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">機械人版的白素貞與許仙現身西湖，引起關注。抖音</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>內地的人形機械人持續受關注，日前便有人將古裝套在機械人身上，變身為高科技版的白素貞和許仙，讓二人在浙江杭州西湖邊重逢，吸引許多網民關注，有人笑指，兩個機械人能舉起雷峰塔，也有人指二「人」造型似拍鬼片。\n\n</p><h2>網民笑指似拍鬼片</h2>\n<p>據快科技9日報道，日前有網民發放影片，聲稱在杭州西湖邊的集賢亭偶遇到了「鋼鐵版」許仙和白娘子浪漫邂逅。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/70d63138f66972250328ed1fdf9143b8/2025-03/152351.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61c6f5ed921023c1c014bbd1aa05b81d/2025-03/15245656.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1767a8318eb94d79b795abf656ffd4ec/2025-03/15516232.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/91fb129142833a4b5e4a2234da33c2a5/2025-03/52656652.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b73252970901b268409226e2978f2b4/2025-03/54145154132.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0a0ebc3378c0c7c894af1d8c268d9589/2025-03/A_456564.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb605f13dc17e90817e736930602a196/2025-03/small_202503090943183368.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4c43750437e4acb9a544a34bfc940737/2025-03/small_202503090943375489.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古裝人形機械人現身西湖邊。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3435514/%E5%AE%87%E6%A8%B9%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E7%8E%8B%E8%88%88%E8%88%88%E5%86%8D%E9%A8%B7%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%AB%E7%89%87-%E8%A4%87%E8%A3%BD%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E9%BE%8D%E6%8B%9B%E7%89%8C%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E8%B8%A2%E9%A3%9B%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%A8%E6%A3%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">宇樹科技︱王興興再騷「機械人功夫片」 複製李小龍招牌動作踢飛對手木棍｜有片</a>\n</p>\n<p>影片顯示，兩台相信是宇樹科技的人形機械人，穿上古裝被扮成白素貞和許仙。\n\n</p>\n<p>鋼鐵版的白素貞和許仙相向而行，互相握手，重會於西湖邊，十分浪漫。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3432662/%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%8A%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%8C%87%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D%E7%8A%AF%E5%94%94%E6%95%A2%E5%8E%BB%E8%9B%87%E5%8F%A3%E5%9B%A0\">北上注意︱機械人警察驚現深圳灣口岸 網民指通緝犯唔敢去蛇口因……</a>\n</p>\n<p>網民看過影片後，紛紛留言，「賽博許仙，白娘子」、「機器人都談戀愛了」、「鋼鐵愛情」等等。也有人指，「感覺像鬼片呢哈哈哈哈」、「千萬不要晚上出來」、「太可愛了，像鬼一樣」。\n\n</p>\n<p>據央視訊介紹，這是央視總台《贏在AI+》節目宣傳片拍攝現場，這是一檔大型紀實創投節目，將於本月中下旬與觀眾見面。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
